      expectedOutput: 'Bag of Words и TF-IDF:\nСловарь: XXX слов\nМатрица BoW: (20, XXX)\nМатрица TF-IDF: (20, XXX)\n\nТоп-5 TF-IDF слов по темам:\n  tech: python (0.XX), code (0.XX), ...\n  sport: team (0.XX), game (0.XX), ...\n\nCosine Similarity (средняя):\n  within topic: 0.XX\n  between topics: 0.XX',
      solution: 'import numpy as np\nfrom sklearn.feature_extraction.text import CountVectorizer, TfidfVectorizer\nfrom sklearn.metrics.pairwise import cosine_similarity\n\ntexts = [\n    "python programming machine learning algorithm data science",\n    "code software developer neural network deep learning model",\n    "database api framework python data analysis visualization",\n    "artificial intelligence computer vision training dataset",\n    "cloud computing server deployment docker kubernetes code",\n    "football team championship goal stadium match player",\n    "basketball game score tournament league season record",\n    "tennis player championship match set victory defeat",\n    "swimming race olympic medal athlete training competition",\n    "marathon runner distance finish personal record time",\n    "pasta recipe italian restaurant cheese sauce cooking",\n    "sushi japanese cuisine fresh fish rice wasabi",\n    "chocolate cake dessert baking sugar butter cream",\n    "salad vegetables healthy nutrition organic diet food",\n    "coffee espresso latte barista beans roasting cafe",\n    "beach resort tropical island vacation paradise relax",\n    "mountain hiking trail adventure backpack camping nature",\n    "city tour museum gallery architecture history culture",\n    "flight airport passport travel luggage destination hotel",\n    "road trip car journey scenic route landscape drive"\n]\ntopics = ["tech"]*5 + ["sport"]*5 + ["food"]*5 + ["travel"]*5\n\n# Bag of Words\ncv = CountVectorizer()\nbow_matrix = cv.fit_transform(texts)\nprint("Bag of Words и TF-IDF:")\nprint(f"Словарь: {len(cv.vocabulary_)} слов")\nprint(f"Матрица BoW: {bow_matrix.shape}")\n\n# TF-IDF\ntfidf = TfidfVectorizer(ngram_range=(1, 2), max_features=200)\ntfidf_matrix = tfidf.fit_transform(texts)\nprint(f"Матрица TF-IDF: {tfidf_matrix.shape}")\n\n# Топ слова по темам\nprint("\\nТоп-5 TF-IDF слов по темам:")\nfeature_names = tfidf.get_feature_names_out()\nfor topic in ["tech", "sport", "food", "travel"]:\n    indices = [i for i, t in enumerate(topics) if t == topic]\n    topic_tfidf = tfidf_matrix[indices].mean(axis=0).A1\n    top_indices = topic_tfidf.argsort()[-5:][::-1]\n    top_words = [(feature_names[idx], topic_tfidf[idx]) for idx in top_indices]\n    words_str = ", ".join([f"{w} ({s:.3f})" for w, s in top_words])\n    print(f"  {topic}: {words_str}")\n\n# Cosine Similarity\nsim_matrix = cosine_similarity(tfidf_matrix)\n\nwithin_sims, between_sims = [], []\nfor i in range(len(texts)):\n    for j in range(i + 1, len(texts)):\n        if topics[i] == topics[j]:\n            within_sims.append(sim_matrix[i, j])\n        else:\n            between_sims.append(sim_matrix[i, j])\n\nprint(f"\\nCosine Similarity (средняя):")\nprint(f"  Внутри темы: {np.mean(within_sims):.4f}")\nprint(f"  Между темами: {np.mean(between_sims):.4f}")\nprint(f"  Разница: {np.mean(within_sims) - np.mean(between_sims):.4f}")\n\nprint(f"\\nПример similarity matrix (первые 4 документа):")\nfor i in range(4):\n    row = " ".join([f"{sim_matrix[i,j]:.2f}" for j in range(4)])\n    print(f"  [{row}]")',
      explanation: 'BoW считает частоты слов — простой baseline. TF-IDF взвешивает: частые в документе, но редкие в корпусе слова получают высокий вес. Ngrams (bigrams) улавливают словосочетания. Cosine similarity между TF-IDF векторами измеряет тематическую близость документов.'
